.SH NAME
pcie_wait_for_link_delay \- Wait until link is active or inactive
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "bool" pcie_wait_for_link_delay
.BI "(struct pci_dev *pdev "  ","
.BI "bool active "  ","
.BI "int delay "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "pdev" 12
Bridge device
.IP "active" 12
waiting for active or inactive?
.IP "delay" 12
Delay to wait after link has become active (in ms)
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Use this to wait till link becomes active or inactive.
